Package: KEGGIdeaMex
Type: Package
Title: Get enriched pathways from KEGG using a list of differentially expressed genes.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: 
  Irving García
  Lorena J. Gómez
  Bernardo M. Quiroga
  Francisco Pérez
  
Maintainer: Francisco Pérez <frpvillatoro@gmail.com>
Description: Returns a list of enriched pathways from a list of differentially expressed genes. 
    It also makes two graphs: one pie chart and a bar plot showing these pathways.
    
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: edgeR, ggplot2, scales, ggmap